            .balance-sales-modal__date 
                span.teacher-black-text-s 20:15 12.10.2020
#teacher-control-withdraw.modal_window
    button(title="Close (Esc)",type="button").mfp-close ×
    .balance-withdraw-modal
        h1.balance-withdraw-modal__title.teacher-block-title Вывод средств
        h2.balance-withdraw-modal__subtitle.teacher-black-text-s Выберите количество средств, которое хотите перевести 
        form(action="#").balance-withdraw-modal__form
            .balance-withdraw-modal__current-amount 
                span.withdraw-current 1505 BYN
                span.withdraw-notice.teacher-grey-text текущий баланс
            .balance-withdraw-modal__how-much 
                span Сумма к выводу
                .balance-withdraw-modal__input-group 
                    input(type="text",placeholder="20000")
                span BYN
            .balance-withdraw-modal__checkbox 
                input(type="checkbox",id="withdrawCheckBox",checked)
                label(for="withdrawCheckBox").balance-withdraw-modal__checkbox-label Я согласен с правилами вывода средств
            .balance-withdraw-modal__buttons 
                a(href="#").teacher-blue-btn Вывести средства
                a(href="#").teacher-grey-btn Отменить вывод